# Source maps — generated for local development (the example app
# consumes the library via `file:../..` and benefits when stepping
# through code) but excluded from the published tarball. They're a
# meaningful chunk of size and most consumers don't use them. Stack
# traces still reference the bundled file path, which is enough for
# bug reports.
dist/**/*.map

